commit.message:
Spotify Playlist Sync

- Change Playback image aspect ratio to 1
- Cache Device ID for Spotify Web Player
- Cache Spotify Profile in Vuex
- Fetch Profile when we don't have it
- Return promise when starting Spotify Web Player
- Optimize Cache Key Store, allowing it to be used without Expiration

Bug Fix
Spotify returns 204 when nothing's playing

Bug Fixes

Spotify Requests
autocomplete no-filter

Auto Config

Using Vue Environment Variables to config URL and Spotify Client Key
Using Auto Config for firebase
Added Slack Notification integration for Travis CI
Update Badge Info && Cache Node Modules

Merge pull request #1 from codacy-badger/codacy-badge

Add a Codacy badge to README.md
